data.description:
Welcome to your own slice of paradise! Nestled on 4 stunning acres, this property offers the perfect blend of privacy and serenity. The perimeter fence and gate provide added security and peace of mind. 
Calling all horse enthusiasts - this is the perfect property for you! With ample space for your beloved equine friends to roam and graze, you'll have all you need to create your own equestrian haven. 
Step inside the spacious well maintained manufactured home and be greeted by 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, the open plan provides plenty of space for family and guests to visit. The oversized porch is perfect for enjoying your morning coffee while taking in the breathtaking views. 
Immerse yourself in the natural beauty of the surroundings, with native trees dotting the landscape. 
Additionally, this property features a well, ensuring a reliable water source year-round. 
Don't miss your chance to own this incredible property with endless possibilities. Contact us today to schedule a viewing.
